snippet.title: Our Darker Purpose -- Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Soon available on Steam, Humble, and www.ourdarkerpurpose.com!

Our Darker Purpose - a procedurally generated, rogue-lite game inspired by Binding of Isaac, Don't Starve, FTL, and a host of other awesome games! Discover the dark secrets of the mysterious Edgewood Home for Lost Children and the plots of the nefarious Administrators!
